trans-unit.source: Provides a list of valid skin IDs for a control at design time, based on the currently applicable theme.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.SkinIDTypeConverter"></xref> class.
Returns a value indicating whether this converter can convert a <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.SkinID*> object to a string using the provided format context and type.
An T:System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext that provides a format context for the control being designed.
A <xref:System.Type>.
<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>, if the conversion can be made; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
Returns a value indicating whether this converter can convert a <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.SkinID*> object to the specified type, using the specified context.
An T:System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext that provides a format context for the control being designed.
A T:System.Type that represents the type to convert to.
<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>, if a conversion can be made; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
Converts the given string to a <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.SkinID*> object using the specified context and culture information.
An T:System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext that provides a format context that represents the control being designed.
A T:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.
If <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> is passed, the current culture is assumed.
The string to convert.
An object that can be cast as a <xref:System.Web.UI.DataSourceControl.SkinID*> object, if the conversion can be made; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
Converts the given <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.SkinID*> object to a string using the specified context and culture information.
An T:System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext that provides a format context that represents the control being designed.
A T:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.
If <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>, the current culture is assumed.
The <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.SkinID*> object to convert.
The T:System.Type to convert `value` to (must be a <xref:System.String>).
An object that represents the converted value.
Returns a set of <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.SkinID*> objects that can be applied to the control that is represented by the given format context.
An T:System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext that provides a format context that represents the control being designed.
`context` or properties of `context` can be <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.

A <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter.StandardValuesCollection?displayProperty=fullName> that holds a set of <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.SkinID*> objects; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>, if the control does not support skins.
Returns a value indicating whether the control that is represented by the given context supports a set of <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.SkinID*> objects that can be picked from a list.
An <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> for the control being designed.

<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>, if <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SkinIDTypeConverter.GetStandardValues*> should be called to find a common set of values the object supports; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
